PRICE NORMALIZATION
Normalized_Price = Price(t) / Price(0)

SPREAD CALCULATION
Spread(t) = Stock_A_normalized(t) - Stock_B_normalized(t)

Z-SCORE (TRADING SIGNAL)
Z-Score(t) = [Spread(t) - Rolling_Mean(30d)] / Rolling_Std(30d)

PEARSON CORRELATION COEFFICIENT
ρ(A,B) = Covariance(Returns_A, Returns_B) / (σ_A × σ_B)
Return(t) = [Price(t) - Price(t-1)] / Price(t-1)

ANNUALIZED VOLATILITY
Volatility = σ_daily × √252

σ_daily = √[1/n × Σ(return_i - mean)²]

252 = number of trading days per year
Pair_Volatility = (Vol_A + Vol_B) / 2

PnL (PROFIT & LOSS) CALCULATION
PnL = Position × (Exit_Spread - Entry_Spread)
Long_spread_position (+1): Buy A, Sell B
Short_spread_position (-1): Sell A, Buy B

PERFORMANCE METRICS
Total_Return = Σ(all PnL trades)
Win_Rate = Number_winning_trades / Total_trades
Volatility_Rank = Rank of volatility (1 = lowest volatility)

VOLATILITY PARADOX TEST
Correlation_Performance_Vol = Corr(Volatility_Rank, Total_Return)




